OL,3,CColour and music at Wrexham's first
OL,4,CAfrican Caribbean festival
OL,6,FIt was Wrexham's first African
OL,7,FCaribbean Festival, but it certainly
OL,8,Fwon't be the last according to
OL,9,Forganisers.
OL,11,FThe event celebrated and showcased the
OL,12,Fvibrant cultures and traditions of the
OL,13,Fgrowing African and Caribbean
OL,14,Fcommunities in North East Wales.
OL,16,FA mix of music and food brought people
OL,17,Ftogether in Wrexham's leafy Bellevue
OL,18,FPark. A bandstand, a temporary home
OL,19,Ffor the DJ's.
