OL,3,CColour and music at Wrexham's first
OL,4,CAfrican Caribbean festival
OL,6,FOmo Idegun founder of Wrexham Africa
OL,7,FCommunity said after opening the
OL,8,Fcity's first Africa shop, the festival
OL,9,Fwas the next obvious step.
OL,11,F"People have been very excited about
OL,12,Fit because this has not happened in
OL,13,FWrexham before. It is bringing the
OL,14,Fcommunity spirit back.
OL,16,F"And is not just Africans and the
OL,17,FCaribbeans, it is people from other
OL,18,Fethnic communities who have come to
OL,19,Fcelebrate with us, which is a very
OL,20,Fgood thing.
