OL,6,F"It is important that we share our
OL,7,Fculture with the mainstream community."
OL,9,FShe said people felt safe to come out
OL,10,Fbecause the environment was friendly
OL,11,Fand welcoming.
OL,13,F"We are brothers and sisters and is is
OL,14,Fso important for us to come together,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
